<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q8_v16" title="Q8_v16" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Registro del caso:</p>
    <p>
      En una planta de producción se prepararán botellitas individuales de un batido de proteínas. La siguiente ficha de producción muestra los ingredientes que lleva cada botellita.
    </p>
    <p>
      Ficha de producción (por cada botellita):<br />
      - Leche: <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> onzas<br />
      - Concentrado de proteína: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas<br />
      Se prepararán en total <m:math><m:mn>240</m:mn></m:math> botellitas de este batido.<br />
      Además, se considera que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> onza</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.<br />
      ¿Cuántos mL de concentrado de proteína se necesitan en total para preparar las botellitas?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">7200 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Cada botellita lleva <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de concentrado, así que para <m:math><m:mn>240</m:mn></m:math> botellitas se necesitan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,75</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>420</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Luego, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>420</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>7200</m:mn></m:math> mL no corresponde al total pedido.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">12600 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El concentrado total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,75</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>420</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> onza</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>420</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. Por eso, la cantidad total de concentrado es <m:math><m:mn>12&#160;600</m:mn></m:math> mL.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">28800 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El problema pregunta solo por el concentrado de proteína. Ese concentrado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas por botellita, entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,75</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>420</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>420</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>28&#160;800</m:mn></m:math> mL no es el total de concentrado solicitado.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">420 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El valor <m:math><m:mn>420</m:mn></m:math> corresponde a onzas, porque <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,75</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>420</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de concentrado. Pero el problema pide mL. Al convertir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>420</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. Por eso, <m:math><m:mn>420</m:mn></m:math> mL no es correcto.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar cuánto concentrado lleva cada botellita</strong></p>
            <p>Cada botellita usa <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de concentrado.</p>
            <p>Pasamos el número mixto a decimal o fracción impropia:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,75</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular las onzas totales de concentrado para 240 botellitas</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1680</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>420</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>En total se necesitan <m:math><m:mn>420</m:mn></m:math> onzas de concentrado.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Convertir onzas a mL</strong></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> onza</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, multiplicamos:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>420</m:mn><m:mtext> onzas</m:mtext><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;600</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>Se necesitan <strong><m:math><m:mn>12&#160;600</m:mn></m:math> mL</strong> de concentrado de proteína en total.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>